{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>告別混亂的補充品攝取，SuppTime: Vitamin Tracker 這款強大的維生素與營養品規劃工具，現在提供終生版限時免費下載，它能精準管理你的每日健康計畫，無論你是僅服用基礎維生素 D 和 Omega-3，或是追求複雜生酮飲食的專業人士，SuppTime 都能提供科學化的指導，讓你井然有序地優化健康日常，把握這次難得的免費機會，立即提升你的健康管理水平。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-100.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>智能補充品組合與時機助手</h2>\n    <p>SuppTime 內建超過 40 種營養品的專家資料庫，提供科學的服用時機建議與潛在交互作用警示，你可以輕鬆選擇預設的增強免疫、提升專注、助眠或延緩衰老等組合，也能從零開始打造專屬個人化的營養方案，並透過每日藥丸追蹤功能，精確記錄每個時段（早晨、早餐、午餐、下午、晚餐、睡前）的攝取情況，確保你的營養補充滴水不漏。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-144-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-145-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-146-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-147-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1284x2778bb-148-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/2048x2732bb-19-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <h2>限時免費領取終生版</h2>\n    <p>這是您免費獲得 SuppTime: Vitamin Tracker 終生版功能的絕佳機會，只需在 App 內完成初始化設定，進入 Settings 內選 Premium，當您看到 Lifetime 價格顯示為 $0 時，即可點擊免費領取。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/IMG_3047-473x1024.webp\" alt=\"IMG 3047\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/IMG_3048-473x1024.webp\" alt=\"IMG 3048\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：SuppTime: Vitamin Tracker</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Health &amp; Fitness</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-27T22:51:41.659272+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":552,"images":9,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}